com.tacticalenterprisesltd

Class CreateEditDeleteOutput

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tacticalenterprisesltd.CreateEditDeleteOutput
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BasicOutput

    public class CreateEditDeleteOutput
extends java.lang.Object
implements BasicOutput
    This class contains the members required to return a response to the client side whenever all processing (filtering, pagination, etc.) is performed on the client side. An instance of this class is passed to the constructor of an instance of GSon for processing as a JSON string. More specifically, it is used only for operations create a new record, edit a record, or delete a record. Unlike NonSSPOutput, it doesn't include the additional members: options and files. For the operations indicated these members are not required.
